goal: your success





Personally Invested®
When you choose a company to work with, you want to know that its employees are personally invested. You want to be sure that your interests are their interests.
For over 75 years, many of the most complex financial institutions in the world have chosen to work with BNY Mellon's Pershing. In an ever-changing marketplace, we have been trusted, tested and proven to protect our clients’ interests while providing them with the most innovative solutions possible. Our clients are leaders in their fields and they choose Pershing because we are a leader in ours.
As a business-to-business provider, we provide global financial solutions to advisors, broker-dealers, family offices, hedge and '40 Act fund managers, registered investment advisor firms and wealth managers. We help our clients power their businesses and maximize opportunities because they can rely on our industry expertise, our innovative solutions and our powerful technology. We provide insightful solutions that help create a competitive advantage for our clients—so they can help provide a more secure financial future for their clients. At Pershing, we never forget that all of our relationships are personal. Every employee we have, every action we take comes back to one core commitment: a personal investment in your success.
Learn more about how you can power your business with our integrated solution set, including:

Clearing, Custody and Settlement
Investment Solutions
Managed Investments
Marketing and Practice Management
Prime Services
Retirement Solutions
Technology and Enterprise Data Management
Trading Services

* Pershing LLC and its global affiliates, March 31, 2017



